name: FrankenButter
description:
Classic Creature #1

Frankenbutter was created on a dark and stormy night, some say out of large amounts of dairy products. This is just a vicious schoolyard rumor that proceeds his voracious appetite of anything covered in the creamy spread; as he stalks the countryside at dusk, breaking into homes and turning over tables looking for buttered toast.

Created in VR, Finished in 3D.
